__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.DS_Store
.env
.env.*
!.env.local.example
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/*.lock
dist/
build/
*.tmp

# Candidate PII and generated artifacts — never push to remote
profile/raw/
# (profile/raw/intake/ — private source dump: old resumes, cover letters,
#  application answers, work journals — is covered by profile/raw/ above.)
profile/normalized/
# Private source-of-truth analysis: source maps, lane recommendations, and any
# other working notes derived from raw material. Local-only, never tracked.
profile/private-review/
data/generated/
data/companies/
data/applications/
data/leads/
data/runs/
data/discovery/
data/calibration/
data/watch/
docs/reports/*-report.md
examples/results/

# Real resume-lane files and the claims truth bank are PII. Track only the
# scaffolding: templates (profile/resumes/templates/), the README, and the
# sanitized example claims bank. See docs/guides/profile-and-resume-privacy.md.
profile/resumes/*.md
!profile/resumes/README.md
profile/claims/*.json
!profile/claims/claims-bank.example.json

# Internal capability/audit reports carry candid personal job-search context.
# Keep them local; never push.
docs/reports/*-audit-*.md

# Generated profile reports (profile-document-audit.md, profile-completeness.md,
# …) are normalized-profile output and carry PII/private source references.
# Regenerated locally by `normalize-profile`; keep them local. README stays tracked.
docs/reports/profile-*.md

# Watchlist contains user-supplied target-company names (PII-adjacent).
# Track config/watchlist.example.yaml as the template.
config/watchlist.yaml

# Local watcher run profiles may reference private prefs paths / cadence.
# Track config/watch-profiles.example.yaml as the template.
config/watch-profiles.yaml

# Batch 4 (Indeed auto-apply) PII-bearing runtime artifacts.
# Template seed `data/answer-bank.seed.json` IS tracked; working copy is not.
data/_intake/
data/answer-bank.json
data/*.bak-*
data/answer-bank-audit.log
data/answer-bank.json.lock
data/gmail-cursor.json
data/applications/**/checkpoints/
data/applications/**/attempts/
data/applications/_suspicious/
data/applications/batches/.lock
docs/reports/answer-bank-pending.md
docs/reports/apply-batch-*.md
